txt.en: Thank you for contributing your collection! Please place your items in the box to receive your reward.
Wanted: Blackened feathers from birds near Amon Raith. Deliver the items to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith.
'Camilla will be pleased to receive these. Thank you.'
'Camilla wanted to do something nice for those of us trapped here at Amon Raith. She said that she needed feathers; thus the request.'
DNT HIDING CONTENT - Task: Blackened Feathers
Nathan Hodges, at Amon Raith, awaits the collection and delivery of blackened feathers.
Deliver the blackened feathers to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith
Wanted: Blackened feathers from birds near Amon Raith.
